      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">9</infon>
        <offset>1082</offset>
        <text>Interestingly, comparable 15N2-fixation rates were measured under light and dark conditions.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">10</infon>
        <offset>1175</offset>
        <text>Meanwhile, phylogenetic analyses for the functional gene biomarker nifH and its transcripts could not detect any common photoautotrophic diazotrophs, such as, Trichodesmium, but a prevalence of gamma-proteobacteria and the unicellular photoheterotrophic Group A cyanobacteria.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">11</infon>
        <offset>1452</offset>
        <text>The dominance of these likely heterotrophic diazotrophs was further verified by quantitative PCR.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">12</infon>
        <offset>1550</offset>
        <text>Hence, our combined results show that the ultra-oligotrophic SPG harbors a hitherto unknown heterotrophic diazotrophic community, clearly distinct from other oceanic gyres previously visited.
</text>
      </sentence>
